ComicInfo.Title: Where No Duck has Gone Before, Sort of!
ComicInfo.Summary: Where No Duck has Gone Before, Sort of!: The local convention center books two popular conventions at the same time, forcing Launchpad and the boys to navigate the massive crowd for the other convention in order to get to the massive crowd attending their convention.
